modules.description: This module provides functions to convert between a structured representation of values and their view in a common format. It works with `Msgpck.t` values and `Json_repr.view` structures, enabling direct transformations and inspections. Concrete use cases include serializing and deserializing data structures for storage or transmission.

This module provides direct conversion between structured values and their representation in a common format, using `Msgpck.t` and `Json_repr.view`. It supports constructing and destructing values via encodings, and defining custom bidirectional transformations with schema support. Concrete use cases include serialization and deserialization of complex data for storage or network transmission.
